  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to examine the effectiveness of telephone cognitive-behavioral
      therapy for subthreshold depression and presenteeism in workplace, in comparison with
      treatment-as-usual (TAU) (which is minimal contact through Employers Assistance Program
      (EAP)).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
